import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './FAQ.css'; export default function FAQ() { const [activeIndex, setActiveIndex] = useState(null); const toggleFAQ = (index) => { setActiveIndex(activeIndex === index ? null : index); }; return (

Frequently Asked Questions

Here are answers to some common questions about Gen AI Editor.

toggleFAQ(0)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

What is Gen AI Editor?

{activeIndex === 0 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Gen AI Editor is a smart, AI-powered platform built by IIT Indore students to simplify video and photo editing using cutting-edge tools.

toggleFAQ(1)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Is it free to use?

{activeIndex === 1 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Yes, the basic tools are free to use. Advanced features may require login or limited access depending on future updates.

toggleFAQ(2)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

What types of editing can I do?

{activeIndex === 2 ? '▲' : '▼'}

You can remove backgrounds from full videos, eliminate objects from image frames, enhance visuals, apply filters, and more.

toggleFAQ(3)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Do I need any experience to use this?

{activeIndex === 3 ? '▲' : '▼'}

No! Gen AI is designed for everyone — from beginners to professionals. It’s simple, intuitive, and fast.

toggleFAQ(4)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Can I upload and edit long videos?

{activeIndex === 4 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Yes. Our backend supports processing full-length videos, although performance may depend on device specs and internet speed.

toggleFAQ(5)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Which AI models power this app?

{activeIndex === 5 ? '▲' : '▼'}

We use Robust Video Matting (RVM), Mask2Former, LaMa, and other state-of-the-art models for accurate and fast editing.

toggleFAQ(6)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Do I need to install anything?

{activeIndex === 6 ? '▲' : '▼'}

No installation is required. The platform is fully browser-based — just visit the site and start editing.

toggleFAQ(7)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Is my data safe?

{activeIndex === 7 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Yes. Your files are temporarily processed and deleted after editing. We don’t store user data.

toggleFAQ(8)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Will there be more tools in the future?

{activeIndex === 8 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Absolutely! We’re working on smart color grading, AI upscaling, motion tracking, and even style transfer tools.

toggleFAQ(9)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Can I suggest a feature?

{activeIndex === 9 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Yes, we welcome suggestions. Just head over to the Contact page and let us know what you’d like to see.

toggleFAQ(10)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

How fast is the processing?

{activeIndex === 10 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Most tasks complete within seconds to a few minutes depending on video size and processing complexity.

toggleFAQ(11)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Can I collaborate or contribute?

{activeIndex === 11 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Yes, we love collaborations! Whether you’re a developer, designer, or just a curious learner, feel free to contact us.

toggleFAQ(12)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Is this app mobile-friendly?

{activeIndex === 12 ? '▲' : '▼'}

The platform works on mobile browsers too, but for best results, we recommend using a desktop/laptop.

toggleFAQ(13)} data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" >

Who built this platform?

{activeIndex === 13 ? '▲' : '▼'}

Gen AI Editor is built by a passionate team of students from IIT Indore, driven to democratize content creation through AI.
